value.0: Kibs, a squinty-eyed hin, indeed.  He appears to display a very fascinating interest in you as you pass by his shop.  A look of pursuasion.
Clothed in a blood-red robe that only accents the crimson fire color of his hair and pale skin, the ever-goggle covered eyes of Muck Magus regard each customer critically.

Dunkar fought as a soldier in countless campaigns. His grim determination in the Horde Wars gave him the nickname "the Gruff".  He lost this addendum after an unfortunate event involving some irrate Orcs in the Amian Frontier, along with his left leg.

Value.value: The Town Hall is where the Mayor does his work!  You can also sign up to become a citizen here if ya like!  There's a gear shop and a magic shop in the turfhouses.  To my west is the 'Hinn Inn'.
